    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到</strong> <strong>Forest Reigns</strong>，这是一款融合 RPG 元素的生存 FPS 游戏，背景设定在被变异森林吞噬的后末日巴黎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>森林：是敌是友？</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不仅仅是环境——它是一种有意识的存在，有着自己的意图和目的。与它互动，揭开深藏的秘密，借助它的力量击败敌人，或者面对它因你选择而来的愤怒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/3df26c9e6113af4e473837bc492d47d6.poster.avif?t=1748252621\" width=720 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/3df26c9e6113af4e473837bc492d47d6.webm?t=1748252621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/3df26c9e6113af4e473837bc492d47d6.mp4?t=1748252621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>揭开黑暗秘密</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在一个非线性叙事的世界中，挑战几十个任务。与独特势力合作或竞争，每一个决定都将影响结局的走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/f2783cd842fe39f532ec2897f0bbc88d.poster.avif?t=1748252621\" width=720 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/f2783cd842fe39f532ec2897f0bbc88d.webm?t=1748252621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/f2783cd842fe39f532ec2897f0bbc88d.mp4?t=1748252621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为 FPS 战斗专家</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验紧张激烈的枪战，享受逼真的武器操控，从丰富的可定制装备中挑选你的战斗利器。升级你的武器库，提升火力和效率，让每一发子弹都精准命中目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/feca05791267a81e137e2d8eabae9027.poster.avif?t=1748252621\" width=720 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/feca05791267a81e137e2d8eabae9027.webm?t=1748252621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/feca05791267a81e137e2d8eabae9027.mp4?t=1748252621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>生存与制作</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >资源稀缺，危机四伏。制作物品、搜刮资源，并提前规划每一步。适应这个绿色的新世界，否则你将成为自然选择的下一个牺牲品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/a66985329235ef22c34e278897946ee1.poster.avif?t=1748252621\" width=720 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/a66985329235ef22c34e278897946ee1.webm?t=1748252621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/a66985329235ef22c34e278897946ee1.mp4?t=1748252621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索重生的巴黎</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现被自然之力重塑的巴黎。目睹那些熟悉的标志性地标在绿色末日下的全新面貌，为你的冒险提供一个既陌生又熟悉的舞台。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/e8df5ac476503a5b7b3e8dcd15ea8a89.poster.avif?t=1748252621\" width=720 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/e8df5ac476503a5b7b3e8dcd15ea8a89.webm?t=1748252621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325070/extras/e8df5ac476503a5b7b3e8dcd15ea8a89.mp4?t=1748252621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个不断变化的世界中，每一个决定都至关重要。与致命的生物搏斗，探索危险且变幻莫测的环境，打造生存必需的工具。射击、掠夺、适应，在这场扣人心弦的冒险中顽强生存下去！</p>",
